# Toker League

> [!INFO] Summary
> A sophisticated fantasy football league website with 18+ years of historical data (2007-2025). Static HTML/CSS/JS frontend powered by a Node.js data synchronization pipeline that keeps Yahoo Fantasy Sports API data aligned with the public-facing website.

