## 🧠 Architecture

### Manifest-Driven System
```
manifest.json (registry)
    ↓
season files (teams.json, matchups.json, draft.json)
    ↓
data.js (lazy-loading cache with IIFE pattern)
    ↓
window.codexData (global API)
    ↓
main.js, team.js, admin.js (UI scripts)
```

### Data Directory
```
assets/statistics/
├── manifest.json         # Registry of all seasons
├── franchises.json       # Franchise identity mapping
├── 2007/                 # Per-season data
│   ├── teams.json        # Normalized team data
│   ├── teams.raw.json    # Raw Yahoo API response
│   ├── matchups.json     # Game-by-game results
│   ├── draft.json        # Draft picks
│   ├── metadata.json     # Season summary
│   └── transactions.json # Waivers & trades
├── 2008/, 2009/, ... 2025/
```

