## 🔧 Development Commands

```bash
# Authentication & Setup
npm run yahoo:auth              # Yahoo OAuth setup
npm run git:configure           # Git auto-commit config

# Data Synchronization
npm run yahoo:sync              # Sync current season
npm run yahoo:sync -- --season 2024     # Specific season
npm run front-office:sync       # Commissioner content

# Local Development
npm install
npx http-server .               # Serve locally (port 8080)
```

### GitHub Actions
- **yahoo-sync.yml** - Runs every 6 hours
- **front-office-sync.yml** - Runs every 30 minutes

